Uses of Package
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind

Packages that use com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge Defines functionality to map bi-directionally between custom POJOs used as representation of Rhizosphere models and equivalent custom-tailored JavaScriptObjects that the underlying Rhizosphere javascript library can understand. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind Definition of Rhizosphere generators that convert POJOs (externally provided by users of this GWT module) into model objects suitable for use by the Rhizosphere underlying javascript library. 
 

Classes in com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind used by com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge
BridgeType
          Annotation attached to BridgeCapabilities.JSO_BUILDER_CLASS methods to define Java type to Rhizosphere kind mapping information.
 

Classes in com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind used by com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind
BridgeCapabilities
          Enumerates the supported mapping capabilities between Java types and equivalent Rhizosphere types for the purpose of converting POJOs into custom tailored JavaScriptObjects usable as Rhizosphere models.
BridgeCapabilities.BridgeMethod
          A method of BridgeCapabilities.JSO_BUILDER_CLASS that can port a specific Java type onto a Rhizosphere model object.
ModelInspector
          Analyzes a POJO class implementing RhizosphereModel and identifies all the attributes that must be ported and exposed into a Rhizosphere visualization built from it.
ModelInspector.MappableMethod
          Accessor method that extracts an attribute from a POJO implementing RhizosphereModel and that needs to be ported to the Rhizosphere model.
